OL,6,FIn Torfaen 10 schools were closed and
OL,7,FBlaenau Gwent 20 shut.
OL,9,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,10,Fhas issued the first amber cold
OL,11,Fweather health alert of the season,
OL,12,Fwarning conditions could be dangerous
OL,13,Ffor vulnerable people, including the
OL,14,Felderly.
OL,16,FNational Rail warned the cold climate
OL,17,Fwould affect various routes on
OL,18,Fnorthern train services until at least
OL,19,F2pm on Tuesday.
