OL,6,FNational Highways also sent out a
OL,7,Fsevere amber weather alert for snow.
OL,9,FDr Agostinho Sousa, from the UKHSA,
OL,10,Fsaid: "This is the first amber Cold
OL,11,FWeather Health Alert of the season,
OL,12,Fbut we can expect more as we approach
OL,13,Fwinter, and it is vital to check in on
OL,14,Fvulnerable friends, family and
OL,15,Fneighbours to ensure they are well
OL,16,Fprepared for the onset of cold
OL,17,Fweather."
OL,19,FParticularly if they are elderly or
OL,20,Fotherwise at increased risk."
